						               													<description>This expansion makes adding a 5th hero to your Bat-team worry free.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Now unleash 4 vs 1 in 3 Adventure mode missions and take Justice to that lawbreaker.&amp;#10;The &amp;ldquo;Detective Comics &amp;ldquo; series by James Tynion IV is the setting for these 3 missions, Batman assembles a new Bat-team led by Batwoman and featuring the skills and talents of Stephanie Brown, Cassandra Cain, Tim Drake and Basil Karlo.&amp;#10;5th player Adventure mode provides the Evil Masterminds side with some much-needed fortitude to stand up to the might of 4 heroes of Gotham. Villains have access to a larger reinforcement point pool and a boosted Energy Cube turn recovery amount, that lays a good foundation towards going toe to toe with the team and instigating their heinous plan.&amp;#10;Careful consideration during setup is key to a villain&amp;rsquo;s victory, as the evil mastermind, you have to ensure that your back up is up to the job. Remember that point when creating your own missions in &amp;rdquo;Mission Maker &amp;ldquo;. Back up, Back, up, back up &amp;ndash; make sure you have some &amp;ndash; tough cookies too.&amp;#10;Setting inspired, Clayfaces&amp;rsquo; hero screen rounds out the expansion and the team, with Batwoman leading the plays &amp;ndash; these 3 missions drop you right into the comics timeline.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Mission 1 &amp;ndash; Our Heroes face off the Court of Owls, aided by Cassandra&amp;rsquo;s father as they plan to awaken an entire army of Talons to wreak chaos and destruction in Gotham City &amp;ndash; it&amp;rsquo;s your job to foil them.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Mission 2 &amp;ndash; The head of the Demon, attended by Deathstroke plans Gotham&amp;rsquo;s downfall. His plan ? take out the city&amp;rsquo;s economic backbone, destroy the corruption it creates. Your Job &amp;ndash; Guard and Prevent.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Mission 3 - The St Dumas Order&amp;rsquo;s final creation is awakening &amp;ndash; the team faces the Azrael assassins and the artificial intelligence Ascalon. It&amp;rsquo;s your job to lay waste to this order once and for all.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;More Missions for this dedicated team will roll out, fully supporting 5 player mode into the future in addition to expanding the mission roster even further.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
